    <item>
      <title>电池主导地位带来红利，宁德时代第一季度净利润增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/catl-first-quarter-net-rises-as-battery-dominance-pays-dividends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宁德时代新能源科技有限公司第一季度利润增长，原因是该电池制造商在全球电动汽车电池供应方面的主导地位抵消了汽车销售疲软的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/catl-first-quarter-net-rises-as-battery-dominance-pays-dividends</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 11:12:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗称爱马仕将超越威登成为最大奢侈品牌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/hermes-can-surpass-vuitton-as-luxury-s-biggest-brand-citi-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团分析师表示，按营业额计算，爱马仕有可能在未来几年超越路威酩轩集团的旗舰店路易威登，成为奢侈品行业营业额最大的品牌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/hermes-can-surpass-vuitton-as-luxury-s-biggest-brand-citi-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 11:04:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金创始人 Sanjay Shah 卷入 14 亿英镑税务骗局审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/hedge-fund-founder-sanjay-shah-on-trial-in-uk-over-1-4-billion-tax-scam</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对冲基金创始人桑杰·沙阿 (Sanjay Shah) 被指控为“精心策划”的 Cum-Ex 交易计划的幕后策划者，该计划在伦敦民事审判开始时诈骗了丹麦政府 14 亿英镑（17 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/hedge-fund-founder-sanjay-shah-on-trial-in-uk-over-1-4-billion-tax-scam</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 10:53:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行 Simkus 预计 2024 年将降息三次，有可能第四次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/ecb-s-simkus-sees-three-rate-cuts-this-year-chance-of-fourth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员格迪米纳斯·西姆库斯表示，借贷成本将从 6 月开始下降——预计 2024 年至少会发生三起此类举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/ecb-s-simkus-sees-three-rate-cuts-this-year-chance-of-fourth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 07:33:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯表示，随着中国紧张局势升级，死亡可能触发美国协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/marcos-says-no-plans-to-grant-us-access-to-more-military-bases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯在与中国关系日益紧张的情况下表示，如果一名菲律宾士兵死于外国袭击，菲律宾将援引与美国的防务条约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/marcos-says-no-plans-to-grant-us-access-to-more-military-bases</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 06:52:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场押注紧张局势缓和，以色列谢克尔反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/israeli-shekel-gains-as-traders-watch-response-to-iran-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者押注伊朗和以色列之间的冲突不会进一步升级，以色列货币在一轮抛售后反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/israeli-shekel-gains-as-traders-watch-response-to-iran-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 06:06:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>避险热潮过后，通胀担忧卷土重来，债券下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/treasuries-haven-role-faces-pressure-from-oil-price-impact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周末前席卷市场的国债买盘正在平息，人们希望伊朗和以色列之间的冲突现在能够平息，人们的注意力又回到了困扰世界经济的通胀压力上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/treasuries-haven-role-faces-pressure-from-oil-price-impact</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 04:26:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Apollo 的亚洲扩张已吸引来自该地区的 350 亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/apollo-s-asia-expansion-has-lured-in-35-billion-from-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 对其亚洲业务的改造已开始取得成效：自 2022 年初以来，该公司已从该地区筹集了 350 亿美元资金以支持扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/apollo-s-asia-expansion-has-lured-in-35-billion-from-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
